#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Kasts"
msgstr "Kasts"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Podcast application"
msgstr "Application de Podcast"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:27
msgid ""
"Kasts is a convergent podcast application that looks good on desktop and "
"mobile."
msgstr ""
"Kasts es un application de podcast convergente que appare belle sur "
"scriptorio e mobile."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:28
msgid "Its main features are:"
msgstr "Su characteristicas principal es:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:30
msgid "Episode management through play queue"
msgstr "Gestion de episodio per cauda de reproduction"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:31
msgid ""
"Sync playback positions with other clients through gpodder.net or gpodder-"
"nextcloud"
msgstr ""
"Synchronisa positiones de reproduction con altere clientes per gpodder.net o "
"gpodder-nextcloud"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:32
msgid "Variable playback speed"
msgstr "Velocitate de repsoduction variabile"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:33
msgid "Search for podcasts"
msgstr "Cerca podcastes"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:34
msgid "Full system integration: e.g. inhibit system suspend while listening"
msgstr ""
"Integration systema complete: p.ex. inhibi suspension de systema quando "
"ascolta"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:51
msgid "Kasts on the desktop with default header bar"
msgstr "Kasts sur le scriptorio con barra de capite predefinite"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:55
msgid "Kasts on the desktop with minimized header bar"
msgstr "Kasts sur le scriptorio conbarra de capite minimisate"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:59
msgid "Kasts on a phone"
msgstr "Kasts sur  un telephono"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:63
msgid "Kasts mobile player controls"
msgstr "Controles de reproductor mobile de Kasts"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:84
msgid ""
"Fixed occasional crashes when updating podcasts after app has been open for "
"a while."
msgstr ""
"Corrigite fracassos occasional quando il actualisa podcasts post que un app "
"ha essite aperite per alcun tempore. "

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:85
msgid "Fixed a crash happening when resetting the sleep timer."
msgstr ""
"Corrigite un fracasso occurrente quando reinitialisante le temporisator de "
"dormir."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:86
msgid "Fixed the sort order functionality on episode lists."
msgstr "Corrigite leordine de ordinar functionalitate sur listas de episodios."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:87
msgid "Fixed visual glitches in the header image and in the subscription list."
msgstr ""
"Corrigite defectos visual in le imagine capite e in le lista de "
"subscriptiones."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:106
msgid "Highlights of changes in 24.02.0:"
msgstr "Punctos in evidentia de cambiamentos in 24.02.0:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:108
msgid "Kasts has been ported to Qt6 and KDE Frameworks 6."
msgstr "Kasts ha essite porteta a Qt6 e KDE Framework 6."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:109
msgid "The color scheme can now be selected manually."
msgstr "Le schema de color pote nunc esser selectionate manualmente."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:110
msgid "Fixed several bugs related to images and playback controls."
msgstr ""
"Corrigite multe faltas affin a imagines e controlos de reproduction "
"(playback)."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:111
msgid "Network checks for metered connections can now be fully disabled."
msgstr ""
"Verificas de rete perconnexiones a consumo pote ora esser completemente "
"dishabilitate."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:112
msgid "Updating podcasts should now be significantly faster on slow hardware."
msgstr ""
"Actualisar podcasts deberea esser ora significativemente plus rapide sur "
"hardware lente."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:129
msgid "New features and bugfixes in this release:"
msgstr "Nove characteristicas e correctiones de faltas in iste version:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:131
msgid ""
"The header bar player controls have been redesigned, partly based on the "
"design of Elisa. The header bar is resizeable and can be fully collapsed to "
"just a minimal toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Le controlos de executor de barra de capite ha essite redesignate, in parte "
"sur le designo de Elisa. Le barra de capite es redimensionabile e pote esser "
"completemente plicate a sol un minime barra de instrumento."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:132
msgid ""
"The left sidebar menu in desktop mode has been redesigned. It's now using "
"similar buttons to the ones used in the bottom navigation bar in mobile mode."
msgstr ""
"Le menu de barra lateral sinistre in modo de scriptorio ha essite "
"redesignate. Il ora usa buttones simile a los usate in le barra de "
"navigation de basso in modo mobile."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:133
msgid ""
"The audio backend has been re-written from scratch. It can now handle "
"multiple backends: libVLC, gstreamer and Qt Multimedia. Kasts will use "
"libVLC as default backend when available, which should solve common issues: "
"volume control is now available through the main toolbar and seeking should "
"no longer make the audio hang."
msgstr ""
"Le retro administration (backend) del audio  ha essite rescribite ex novo. "
"Il pote ora manear multiple backends:  libVLC, gstreamer e Qt Multimedia. "
"Kasts usara libVLC como backend predefinite quando disponibile, lo que "
"deberea solver problemas commun: controlode volumine es nunc disponibile "
"trans le barra de instrumento principal e le cercar (seeking) non deberea "
"plus facer que le audio se interrumpe. "

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:134
msgid "The settings menu was ported to the new form components."
msgstr "Le menu de preferentias esseva portate al nove componentes de forma."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:135
msgid "Support for chapter images was added."
msgstr "Supporto perimagines de capitulo esseva addite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:136
msgid ""
"Timestamps mentioned in episode descriptions are now clickable, which will "
"make the audio jump to that point in the episode."
msgstr ""
"Le marcas temporal mentionate in descriptiones de episodio es ora "
"cliccabile, lo que facerà possibile saltar  a ille puncto in le episodio."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:137
msgid ""
"Images in headers are now clickable. This will open a fullscreen view of the "
"image in question."
msgstr ""
"Imagines in capites es nunc cliccabile. Isto aperira un vista de schermo "
"plen del imagine in question."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:138
msgid ""
"The subscribe button is now disabled when a podcast has just been added."
msgstr ""
"Le button de subscriber es nunc dishabilitate quandoun podcast ha essite "
"justo addite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:139
msgid "Several issues with right-to-left language layouts were solved."
msgstr ""
"Multe problemas con dispositiones de linguage de dextera a sinistra esseva "
"solvite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:150
msgid ""
"The interface is simplified by only showing one page at a time instead of "
"adding columns, and by combining the podcast page with the podcast episode "
"list page."
msgstr ""
"Le interfacie es simplificate permonstrar solmente un pagina alvice in loco "
"de adder columnas,e per combinar le pagina de podcast con le pagina de lista "
"de episodio de podcast."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:151
msgid ""
"The podcast and episode info pages are improved by adding a button toolbar "
"(moving actions out of the app header) and by reworking the information "
"layout."
msgstr ""
"Le paginas de info de podcast e episodio ed meliorate per adder un barr  de "
"instrumento de button (movente actiones foras delcapite del app) e per "
"reelaborar le disposition de information."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:152
msgid "A sleep timer has been implemented."
msgstr "Un temporisator de dormir ha essite implementate."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:153
msgid "The app will now remember the position and size of its window."
msgstr "Leappnunc memorera le position e grandor de su fenestra"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:154
msgid ""
"Kasts now has the ability to push all local episode states to the sync "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Kasts nunc ha le habilitate a pulsar omne statos de episodio local al "
"servitor de sync."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:155
msgid ""
"A setting has been added to tell Kasts how many recent episodes should be "
"marked as unplayed when adding a new podcast."
msgstr ""
"Un preferentia ha essite addite per dicer a Kasts comomulte episodios "
"recente deberea esser marcate como non reproducite quando on adde un nove "
"podcast."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:156
msgid "Several small UI bugs and glitches were solved."
msgstr "Multe parve faltas de UI e problemas esseva solvite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:164
msgid ""
"The podcast update routine has been completely overhauled, solving several "
"bugs. It's now using multithreading, and it will also update existing "
"episode information."
msgstr ""
"Le routine de actualisar de podcast ha essite completemente refacite, "
"solvente multe faltas.Ilnunc esusante multithreading, e il tamben "
"actualisara information  de episodio existente."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:165
msgid ""
"General improvements were made to make sure that the app fits well on small "
"screens in both portrait and landscape mode."
msgstr ""
"Meliorementos general esseva facite pro facer secur que le app se adapta ben "
"sur parve schermosin ambes modo de orientation verticale horizontal."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:166
msgid "Episode images will now be retrieved from id3v2tag if available."
msgstr ""
"Imagines de episodio essera nunc recuperate ex  id3v2tag si disponibile."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:167
msgid ""
"New episodes will be added to the queue in ascending chronological order "
"(rather than descending) per podcast."
msgstr ""
"Nove episodios essera addite alcauda in ordine chronologic ascendente (plus "
"tosto que descendente) per podcast."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:168
msgid ""
"A switch has been introduced to optionally adjust the time left on episodes "
"based on the current playback rate."
msgstr ""
"Un commutator ha essite introducite per adaptar optionalmente le tempore "
"lassate sur episodios basate sur le taxa currente de reproduction."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:169
msgid ""
"The episode details pages now have a context action to go straight to the "
"list of episodes for that podcast."
msgstr ""
"Le paginas de detalios de episodio,nunc ha un action de contexto per vader "
"directe al lista de episodios per ille podcast."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:170
msgid ""
"It's now possible to sync with custom GPodder servers (i.e. other than the "
"official gpodder.net instance)."
msgstr ""
"Il es ora possibilesynchronisar con servitores de GPodder personalisate (i."
"e. altere que le instantia official de  gpodder.net)."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:171
msgid ""
"Podcasts can now again be updated even when the sync server is unavailable. "
"This was a bug in previous versions."
msgstr ""
"Podcasts pote ora novemente esser actualiste anque quando le servitor de "
"synchronisation non es disponibile. Isto esseva un falta nel version "
"precedente."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:179
msgid "General code quality improvements and bugfixes"
msgstr "Melioramentos general de qualitate de codice e correctiones de faltas"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:187
msgid "Various User interface improvements"
msgstr "Varie perfectionamentos de interfacie de usator"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:188
msgid "Keep fetching episode actions until we get the current timestamp"
msgstr ""
"Mantene cerca de actiones de episodio usque nos obtene le marca de tempore "
"currente"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:189
msgid "Re-enable icons for gpodder and nextcloud"
msgstr "Re-habilita icones per gpodder e nextcloud"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:195 org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:215
msgid "New features in this release:"
msgstr "Nove characteristicas in iste version:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:197
msgid ""
"Support for chapters, both RSS feed and MP3 tags encoded chapters are "
"supported"
msgstr ""
"Supporto per capitulos, capitulos codificate de ambes  syndication RSS e "
"etiquettas MP3 es supportate "

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:198
msgid "Several improvements in user interface"
msgstr "Multe perfectionamentos in interfacie de usator"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:199
msgid "Optimization and improvements for backend"
msgstr "Optimization e perfectionamentos per retro administration (backend)"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:200
msgid "Reworked settings page"
msgstr "Pagina de preferentias reelaborate"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:201
msgid ""
"Support for syncing subscriptions and episode play position using gpodder."
"net or nextcloud-gpodder app"
msgstr ""
"Supporto per synchronisar subscriptiones e position de reproducer episodio "
"usante app de gpodder.net o nextcloud-gpodder"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:202 org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:223
msgid "Several bugfixes."
msgstr "Multe correctiones de faltas."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:209
msgid ""
"Next to some minor bugfixes, it is now possible to change the location where "
"the downloaded podcast episodes and cached images are saved. These files can "
"take up a lot of disk space, so it's nice to be able to store them elsewhere "
"on systems with limited home folder disk space. The related settings now "
"show the disk space used by episodes and images, and allow to clear the "
"image cache."
msgstr ""
"Apud alcun correctiones minor de faltas, il es nunc possibile cambiar le "
"location ubi le episodios de podcast discargate e imagines ponite in cache "
"es salveguardate. Iste files pote prentìder multe spatio de disco, assi il "
"es agradabile esser capace a immagazinar los alibi sur systemas con limitate "
"spatio de disco de dossier domo. Le preferentias affin nunc monstra le "
"spatio de disco usate per episodioe e imagines, e te permitte clarar le "
"cache de imagine."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:217
msgid "Discover page to search for podcasts on podcastindex.org"
msgstr "Pagina de disporerir per cercar podcasts sur podcastindex.org"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:218
msgid "Podcast downloads can now be resumed."
msgstr "Discargamentos depodvasts ora pote esser reprendite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:219
msgid "Updated playback speed settings dialog."
msgstr "Actualisate le Dialogo de preferentias de velocitate de reproduction. "

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:220
msgid "Settings to allow/disallow network access on metered connections."
msgstr ""
"Preferentias per permitter/non permitter accesso de rete sur connexione a "
"consumo."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:221
msgid ""
"More descriptive error notifications from which the complete list of errors "
"can be opened."
msgstr ""
"Notificationes de error plus descriptive ab le qual le lista complete de "
"errores pote esser aperite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:222
msgid "Several smaller improvements: menu item highlighting, tooltips, hotkeys"
msgstr ""
"Multe parve perfectionamentos: evidentias de elemento de menu, consilios de "
"instrumento,claves calide(hotkeys)"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:230
msgid ""
"First release of Kasts, a Kirigami-based convergent podcast player. Released "
"as part of Plasma Mobile Gear 21.06. It features:"
msgstr ""
"Prime version (release) de Kasts,un executor de podcast convergente basate "
"sur Kirigami. Relaxate como parte de Plasma Mobile Gear 21.06. Il presenta:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:232
msgid "a play queue"
msgstr "un cauda a reproducer"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:233
msgid "notification panel and lockscreen media controls"
msgstr "pannello de notification e controlos de media de bloco de schermo"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:234
msgid "inhibits systemd suspend while listening to podcasts"
msgstr "inhibi suspension de systema quando ascolta podcasts"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kasts.appdata.xml:235
msgid "convergent UI; looks good on mobile and desktop"
msgstr "UI convergente: ilsemblabon sur mobile e scriptorio"

